Frequently Asked Questions

Q: Why won't my train start?
A: Make sure you're holding the driver key and have correctly clicked the train control panel

Q: What should I do if screen doors won't open?
A: Right-click the screen doors with the screen door key

Q: Why does the signal always show red?
A: Check if tracks are properly connected and ensure the path ahead isn't blocked

